column2: select count(g.z) as num From specobj g, photoobj s, galspecextra p, emissionlinesport f, stellarMassStarformingport n Where f.specobjID=g.specobjID and g.specobjID=s.specobjID and s.specobjID=p.specobjID and p.specobjID=n.specobjID and (g.legacy_target1& (#|#|#))># and (g.z>=# and g.z<=#)
